text: FK Spartak Bánovce nad Bebravou is a Slovak football team, based in the town of Bánovce nad Bebravou. The club was founded in 1931. ==References== == External links == *Official website *at europrofit.sk Spartak Banovce nad Bebravou Category:1931 establishments in Slovakia
